<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.2.0">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://seungeonk.github.io/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="https://seungeonk.github.io/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2021-02-03T16:52:09-05:00</updated><id>https://seungeonk.github.io/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Seungeon</title><subtitle>Undergrad in University of Virginia, Charlottesville</subtitle><author><name>Seungeon Kim</name><email>sk6qk@virginia.edu</email></author><entry><title type="html">2/3 Sorting and Some Algorithm Principles</title><link href="https://seungeonk.github.io/cs4102%20algorithms/cs4102/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="2/3 Sorting and Some Algorithm Principles" /><published>2021-02-03T00:00:00-05:00</published><updated>2021-02-03T00:00:00-05:00</updated><id>https://seungeonk.github.io/cs4102%20algorithms/cs4102</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://seungeonk.github.io/cs4102%20algorithms/cs4102/">&lt;h1 id=&quot;sorting-terms&quot;&gt;Sorting Terms&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Comparison Sort&lt;/strong&gt;: 키를 비교하여 아이템을 움직인다&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Adjacent Sort&lt;/strong&gt;: 근접한 요소(adjacent elements)를 움직임으로 정렬하는 알고리즘
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;bubble, insertion 등등&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stable Sort&lt;/strong&gt;: Sorting 알고리즘이 Stable(안정)하다
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;when two items x and y occur in the relative order x,y in the original list AND x==y, &lt;strong&gt;then x and y appear in the same relative order x,y in the final sorted list.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In-Place Sort&lt;/strong&gt;: 알고리즘이 &lt;strong&gt;최대 Θ(1)&lt;/strong&gt; 추가 공간을 사용한다
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;e.g. allocating another array of size θ(n) is &lt;strong&gt;NOT&lt;/strong&gt; allowed.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;it doesn’t create any D.S. or so
        &lt;ul&gt;
          &lt;li&gt;ex) 만약 이 알고리즘이 array size 10인 scratch array를 만들면 -&amp;gt; it’s okay! because the space complexity is θ(1).&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
      &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;insertion-sort삽입-정렬&quot;&gt;Insertion Sort(삽입 정렬)&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategy:&lt;/strong&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;First section of list is sorted (say i-1 items)&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Increase this partial solution by…&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Shifting down next item beyond sorted section (i.e. the ith item) down to its proper place in sorted section.  (Must shift items up to make room.)&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Since one item alone is already sorted, we can put steps 1-3 in a loop going from the 2nd to the last item.&lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;
        &lt;h2 id=&quot;python-example&quot;&gt;python example&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;

    &lt;div class=&quot;language-python highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;insertion_sort&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;lst&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;):&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;len&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;lst&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;j&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ow&quot;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;range&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;):&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# lists start at index 0 to n-1
&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;key&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;lst&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;j&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
   &lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# Insert lst[j] into sorted sub-list lst[0:j-1]
&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;j&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ow&quot;&gt;and&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;key&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;lst&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;]:&lt;/span&gt;
          &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;lst&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;lst&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# shift item up
&lt;/span&gt;          &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;lst&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;key&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# put item in correct spot
&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;insertion-sort-analysis&quot;&gt;Insertion Sort: Analysis&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Worst Case :&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;merge-sort&quot;&gt;Merge Sort&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;\(\sum_{a}^{b}(\alpha \pm \beta)\)&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Seungeon Kim</name><email>sk6qk@virginia.edu</email></author><category term="cs4102 algorithms" /><category term="python" /><category term="algorithm" /><category term="sort" /><summary type="html">Sorting Terms Comparison Sort: 키를 비교하여 아이템을 움직인다 Adjacent Sort: 근접한 요소(adjacent elements)를 움직임으로 정렬하는 알고리즘 bubble, insertion 등등 Stable Sort: Sorting 알고리즘이 Stable(안정)하다 when two items x and y occur in the relative order x,y in the original list AND x==y, then x and y appear in the same relative order x,y in the final sorted list. In-Place Sort: 알고리즘이 최대 Θ(1) 추가 공간을 사용한다 e.g. allocating another array of size θ(n) is NOT allowed. it doesn’t create any D.S. or so ex) 만약 이 알고리즘이 array size 10인 scratch array를 만들면 -&amp;gt; it’s okay! because the space complexity is θ(1).</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">2/4 What is software engineering?</title><link href="https://seungeonk.github.io/cs3420%20adv%20software%20dev/what-_is_software_engineering/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="2/4 What is software engineering?" /><published>2021-02-03T00:00:00-05:00</published><updated>2021-02-03T00:00:00-05:00</updated><id>https://seungeonk.github.io/cs3420%20adv%20software%20dev/what%20_is_software_engineering</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://seungeonk.github.io/cs3420%20adv%20software%20dev/what-_is_software_engineering/">&lt;h1 id=&quot;intro&quot;&gt;Intro&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;HCI is kind of psy branch&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This(software engineering)&lt;/strong&gt; is a bit more business branch&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;software is very different&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;h5 id=&quot;key-point-to-remember-programming-is-actually-a-small-part-of-software-engineering&quot;&gt;key point to remember: Programming is actually a small part of software engineering&lt;/h5&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;S.E. is literally the field of how to engineer software&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;EX) building a building
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;knowing how to hammer a nail and how to lay a brick is not enough&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;What else is needed?&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;high-level-se&quot;&gt;High Level S.E.&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;at-a-high-level-se는-steps-of-the-development-process를-생각함&quot;&gt;At a high level, SE는 steps of the development process를 생각함&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Requirements(how do we know what to build?)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Design / Specification&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Programming / Construction / Implementation&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Testing (Verification and Validation)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Production and Release&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Maintenance and Updates(bugs etc)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;why-is-se-different&quot;&gt;Why is S.E. different?&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;What makes creating software different than creating other things that engineers build (ex. machines, aircraft, bridges etc)?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Software is changeable&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Requirements often change DURING development&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Requirements often change AFTER development&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Misconceptions regarding actual time frames / how software is built and maintained from customers… and developers&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;problems-about-failure&quot;&gt;Problems about failure&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;how do we protect software from being failed?&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;how do we make sure the software is safe?
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;ex) HealthCare.gov failed launch&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;find-some-failures&quot;&gt;Find some failures&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Find a major issues making software crashed&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;What was the technical cause?&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;What was the underlying cause?
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;A problem with requirements?&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;No enough testing?&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Training?&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;How would you mitigate this in the future?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content><author><name>Seungeon Kim</name><email>sk6qk@virginia.edu</email></author><category term="cs3420 adv software dev" /><summary type="html">Intro</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">자바스크립트 콜백 함수(JS callback)</title><link href="https://seungeonk.github.io/JS_callback/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="자바스크립트 콜백 함수(JS callback)" /><published>2021-01-29T00:00:00-05:00</published><updated>2021-01-29T00:00:00-05:00</updated><id>https://seungeonk.github.io/JS_callback</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://seungeonk.github.io/JS_callback/">&lt;h2 id=&quot;콜백이란callback&quot;&gt;콜백이란?(Callback)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;i-will-be-back-later&quot;&gt;I will be back later!&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Let’s look at more examples of passing functions as values and using function expressions.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We’ll write a function &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;ask(question, yes, no)&lt;/code&gt; with three parameters:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-js highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;ask&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;question&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;yes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;no&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;confirm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;question&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;))&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;yes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;no&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;();&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;showOk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;alert&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;You agreed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;showCancel&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;alert&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;You canceled the execution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;// usage: functions showOk, showCancel are passed as arguments to ask&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;ask&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;Do you agree?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;showOk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;showCancel&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;여기서 &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;ask&lt;/code&gt;에 들어가는 인자(arguments) 중, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;showOk&lt;/code&gt;와 &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;showCanel&lt;/code&gt; 이 콜백 함수(callback function) 혹은 콜백(callback)이라 불린다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;기본적인 아이디어는, 우리가 함수를 pass하고 나중에 필요할 때, 다시 부른다(expected to be called back later if necessary)는 것이다!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;위의 예시에서, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;showOk&lt;/code&gt;는 &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;yes&lt;/code&gt;의 콜백이 되고, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;showCancel&lt;/code&gt;은 &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;no&lt;/code&gt;의 콜백이 되는 것이다.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;콜백의 기본적 정의는:&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;em&gt;A callback is a function passed as an argument to another function.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;주의&quot;&gt;!주의!&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;callback은 argument로 pass될 때, 괄호(parenthesis)를 뗀다&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ex):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;language-js highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;myDisplayer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;some&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;document&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;getElementById&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;demo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;innerHTML&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;some&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;myCalculator&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;num1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;num2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;myCallback&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;sum&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;num1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;num2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;myCallback&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;sum&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;// no () for myDisplayer&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;myCalculator&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;myDisplayer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;언제-주로-사용when-to-use&quot;&gt;언제 주로 사용?(When to use?)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;주로 비동기 함수(asynchronous functions), 즉 한 함수가 다른 함수를 기다릴 때(파일들을 로드할 때) 등에 주로 사용된다.&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Seungeon Kim</name><email>sk6qk@virginia.edu</email></author><summary type="html">콜백이란?(Callback) I will be back later!</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">HTML Name 속성 vs ID 속성</title><link href="https://seungeonk.github.io/Post_request_name_vs_id/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="HTML Name 속성 vs ID 속성" /><published>2021-01-29T00:00:00-05:00</published><updated>2021-01-29T00:00:00-05:00</updated><id>https://seungeonk.github.io/Post_request_name_vs_id</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://seungeonk.github.io/Post_request_name_vs_id/">&lt;h2 id=&quot;name-속성name-attribute&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Name&lt;/strong&gt; 속성(Name Attribute)&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(Important)&lt;/strong&gt; The name attribute is &lt;strong&gt;used in the HTTP request&lt;/strong&gt; sent by your browser to the server as a variable name associated with the data contained in the value attribute.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Valid only on &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;a&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;form&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;iframe&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;img&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;map&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;input&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;select&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;textarea&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Name&lt;/strong&gt; does not have to be unique, and can be used to group elements together such as radio buttons &amp;amp; checkboxes&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;id-속성id-attribute&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ID&lt;/strong&gt; 속성(ID Attribute)&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Valid on &lt;strong&gt;any element except&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;base&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;html&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;head&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;meta&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;param&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;script&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;style&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;title&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Each Id should be unique&lt;/strong&gt; in the page as rendered in the browser, which may or may not be all in the same file&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is referenced in &lt;strong&gt;CSS&lt;/strong&gt; or &lt;strong&gt;URL&lt;/strong&gt; with &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;#&lt;/code&gt; sign&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is referenced in &lt;strong&gt;JS&lt;/strong&gt; with &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;getElementById()&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Seungeon Kim</name><email>sk6qk@virginia.edu</email></author><summary type="html">Name 속성(Name Attribute)</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">장고 view와 url(Django View and URL)</title><link href="https://seungeonk.github.io/cs3240%20adv%20soft%20dev/django_view/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="장고 view와 url(Django View and URL)" /><published>2021-01-17T00:00:00-05:00</published><updated>2021-01-17T00:00:00-05:00</updated><id>https://seungeonk.github.io/cs3240%20adv%20soft%20dev/django_view</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://seungeonk.github.io/cs3240%20adv%20soft%20dev/django_view/">&lt;h2 id=&quot;django에서-url를-통해-view를-호출하는-방법&quot;&gt;Django에서 Url를 통해 View를 호출하는 방법&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;사용가자 웹사이트에 페이지를 요청할때, Django는 &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;project_name.urls&lt;/code&gt; 파이썬 모듈을 먼저 불러옴&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;project_name.urls&lt;/code&gt;에서 &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;urlpatterns&lt;/code&gt;라는 변수를 찾고, 순서대로 패턴을 훑어감(traverse in order)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;맞는 url(예: &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&apos;polls/&apos;&lt;/code&gt;)를 찾고 나서, 찾은 url text(&lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&apos;polls/&apos;&lt;/code&gt;)를 제거하고 남아있는 텍스트를 보냄(ex: &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&apos;34/&apos;&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;맞는 텍스트를 발견하면(&lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&apos;&amp;lt;int:question_id&amp;gt;/&lt;/code&gt;), &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;detail()&lt;/code&gt;뷰를 콜함&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Seungeon Kim</name><email>sk6qk@virginia.edu</email></author><category term="cs3240 adv soft dev" /><summary type="html">Django에서 Url를 통해 View를 호출하는 방법</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Markdown Syntax Practice</title><link href="https://seungeonk.github.io/MD-Practice/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Markdown Syntax Practice" /><published>2021-01-16T00:00:00-05:00</published><updated>2021-01-16T00:00:00-05:00</updated><id>https://seungeonk.github.io/MD-Practice</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://seungeonk.github.io/MD-Practice/">&lt;h2 id=&quot;this-is-a-practice-for-markdown-syntax&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is a practice for Markdown syntax&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;h6 id=&quot;header-6the-smallest&quot;&gt;header 6(The smallest)&lt;/h6&gt;
&lt;h5 id=&quot;header-5&quot;&gt;header 5&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;header-4&quot;&gt;header 4&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;header-3&quot;&gt;header 3&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;header-2&quot;&gt;header 2&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;header-1the-largest&quot;&gt;header 1(The largest)&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;수평선: 내용을 명시적으로 구분하고 싶을때&lt;/strong&gt;  &lt;strong&gt;’—‘를 입력&lt;br /&gt;
When you need a horizontal line, type ‘—‘&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;엔터키: 라인 바꾸고 싶을 때, ‘엔터 두번’&lt;/strong&gt;  &lt;strong&gt;when you change line, ‘enter twice’&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;강조emphasis&quot;&gt;강조(Emphasis)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Italic = &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;*something*&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;_(something)_&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
ex) &lt;em&gt;hello&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;bold = &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;**something**&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;__something__&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
ex) &lt;strong&gt;bold&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;strikestroke = &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;~~(something)~~&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
ex) &lt;del&gt;strikestroke&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;highlight = &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;u&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/u&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
ex) &lt;u&gt;highlight&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;block-code-insertion&quot;&gt;Block Code Insertion&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;pre&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/pre&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;code&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/code&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; html tag로 변환&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;`&lt;/code&gt;를 3번 입력하고 코드 종류도 적음&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;javascript:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;language-javascript highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;func_a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;hello&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;dl&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;python:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;language-python highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&quot;hello world&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;bash:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;language-bash highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;emacs ~/.zshrc
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;If no language is specified, no syntax highlighting
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;etc&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Seungeon Kim</name><email>sk6qk@virginia.edu</email></author><summary type="html">This is a practice for Markdown syntax</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">first post</title><link href="https://seungeonk.github.io/first/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="first post" /><published>2021-01-16T00:00:00-05:00</published><updated>2021-01-16T00:00:00-05:00</updated><id>https://seungeonk.github.io/first</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://seungeonk.github.io/first/">&lt;h1 id=&quot;first-blog&quot;&gt;First Blog&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;first blog!&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Seungeon Kim</name><email>sk6qk@virginia.edu</email></author><summary type="html">First Blog</summary></entry></feed>